headline.main: ADDITIONAL FOREIGN NEWS.; THE AFRICA'S MAILS.

docs.lead_paragraph: The European mails by the steamship Africa arrived here soon after midnight. The steamer reached her dock at Boston yesterday morning. We make a few interesting extracts. From the Crimea. The news from the Crimea is not very important. The works outside Sebastopol are progressing towards completion.

headline.main: SOUTH AMERICA.; Paraguay and Brazil--The Pacific Squadron--Government Economy--Jobbing and Speculation--A fine article of Sperm Candies.

docs.lead_paragraph: It is a common thing to hear Americans speak of the robbing propensities of Brazilian officials. But it is not so generally known by the people at home that we have as perfectly systematized plans of robbery as any nation on the face of the earth. Take for example, the contract system for furnishing supplies for the Navy.

headline.main: DICK TINTO ON HIS TRAVELS.; Christmas Eve in Italy-American Turnouts--Varieties.

docs.lead_paragraph: In Italy, as elsewhere, Christmas begins on Christmas Eve. So we-that is, about thirty Americans, half of them young ladies between sixteen and twenty-agreed to meet at midnight mass and have a good time of it. Out of a variety of Churches, all of them offering some peculiar attraction, either of music, or illumination, or fashion, we chose La Santissima Annunziata.
